snippet.title: UFO's (U.F.O.s - 1997)(Artech Digital Entertainment) - walkthrough
snippet.description:
UFO's (aka U.F.O.s) 
Published by Corel Corporation, Hoffmann + Associates Inc. 
Developed by Artech Digital Entertainment, Ltd. 

The developers describe it as a "Wacky Hillbilly Space Adventure Game". You'll play the part of the alien "Gnap", who gets stranded on earth, his spaceship wrecked. There must be a way out of even that situation, no doubt. Your job is to find all necessary parts to repair the ship and bring the strange little guy back in the air. 
https://www.mobygames.com/game/windows/ufos
